title: XVIII Century Painting (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Eighteenth Century Painting
Funk & Wagnalls | 1968 | ISBN: N/A | English | 214 pages | PDF | 27 MB


The richness and variety of eighteenth-century painting is beautifully shown in this book with sixty-five color photographs. An Evidence and Documents section sheds light on the works of Diderot, Hogarth, Reynolds and their contemporaries' works. Eighteenth Century Painting includes a chronology of important historical events, a list of museums and an in-depth dictionary of terms, works, artists and a bibliography
